Name: calcium metabolism disease
Definition: A bone remodeling disease that has_material_basis_in a vitamin D deficiency which results_in softening located_in bone.

Name: iron metabolism disease
Definition: An intestinal benign neoplasm that is located_in the colon.

Name: phosphorus metabolism disease

Name: obsolete hypercholesterolemia
Definition: A respiratory system benign neoplasm that derives_from smooth muscle cells and is located_in the trachea.

Name: hypokalemia
